@node 1 "Introduction"

Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~

This program was created to enhance MAX's BBS beyond belief!!!

It is a run time patcher that replaces over 200 functions in the original 
MAXsBBS program :)))

These include:-

	Public Screen ID  (Run almost any program on the MAX's Pro screen!)
	Faster Screen/Window support
	Faster ANSI
	Extended Door support :)
	
	+ Extra features in the registered version :)
	
Doors now have access to internal configs easily, and can place their own
windows/GUI's on the main screen without any dodgy hacks, so programs
produced for MAX's Pro will look more professional :) 

@endnode

@node 2 "Installing"

Installing
~~~~~~~~~~

Installing MAX's BBS Pro is very easy :)))

Simply copy the MAXsPro file to your BBS: dir!  That's it!

This version is CLI/Shell only, do not attach an icon to the program.

When run, it loads up the original MAXsBBS file, patches it and runs the
new version :)

MAx's Pro only works with the 68000 version of MAX's!!!!!
You may use either MAX's v1.54 or v1.5R with this program.

** The un-registered version will not allow parameters to be passed to MAX's.

@endnode

@node 3 "Registering :)))"

To register MAX's BBS Pro, print out the registration form in this archive,
fill it in and send to the following address with ฃ3uk or $5US dollars:-

	Niki Murkett
	4 Northway
	Thatcham
	Berkshire
	RG18 3FG
	England
	
Registering gets you:-

	Configuration Editor
	Un-restricted MAX's Pro
	Multi-node version of MAX's Pro
	Faster screen/window routines (Up to 400% faster than before!)
	Doesn't crash at midnight
	Allows parameters to be passed to MAX's
	Any bug fixes that may appear in the un-registered version.
	+ Some support utils :)

	And more complete docs & developer files :)

** Remember!  If sending cash through the post, selotape coins to a piece
of card, place in a thick envelope and send by recorded delivery!!!!!

If you don't and it gets stolen, I can't send out a registered copy!!!

You get the choice of having the archive uploaded to your BBS (UK ONLY), or
UUencoded and sent via Email :)

A sensible idea would be for sysops who live near each other to club 
together and register 5 or 10 copies at a time if sending cash!
This saves sending coins through the post :)

If buying in bulk, print out multiple copies of the registration form, and
on a extra form, just write where to send all copies too :)

Money accepted can be either cash or cheque, made payable to Niki Murkett.
If sending foriegn currency (US dollars), please send cash as banks charge
huge rates of money to exchange foriegn cheques etc!

@endnode

